# Credit Card Fraud Detection

## Description

Machine Learning project to detect fraudulent credit card transactions.

## Technologies

- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Scikit-learn
- Imbalanced-learn
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn

## Model

Logistic Regression

## Features

- Data preprocessing
- Missing value checking
- Class balancing using SMOTE
- Fraud prediction
- Confusion Matrix
- ROC-AUC Score

## Dataset

creditcard.csv